  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in Senate", 
    "date": "2019-07-16T04:00:00Z", 
    "text": "Skin in the Game Act\n\nThis bill requires each institution of higher education\u00a0(IHE) participating in the federal direct student loan program to pay 50% of\u00a0any student loan balance that is in default for a loan that was used toward the cost of attendance at such IHE.\n\nAn IHE may not increase the costs of attendance in order to offset its liability to pay such balances."
  }, 
